data.description: The perfect countryside retreat - a beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath home nestled on 8 acres in Royal. This move-in ready home has an open concept layout with spacious kitchen and living room, complete with modern appliances and ample natural light.  Spacious primary bedroom featuring an en-suite bathroom with a walk-in shower and luxurious garden tub.  This property offers endless possibilities for outdoor activities such as gardening, hiking, or a few farm animals.  Horseback riding trails are just around the corner!
